quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  19,96,"Mu by’ukuri abemeye bakanakora ibyiza, (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe azabahundagazaho urukundo rwe, (anabahe gukundwa n’abagaragu be)"
  19,97,"Mu by’ukuri, (Qur’an) twarayoroheje tuyishyira mu rurimi rwawe (yewe Muhamadi) kugira ngo uyikoreshe ugeza inkuru nziza ku batinya Allah, ndetse unayikoreshe uburira abantu b’abahakanyi"
  19,98,Nonese ni ibisekuru bingahe twarimbuye mbere yabo! Ese hari n’umwe muri bo ukibona cyangwa ngo wumve akoma
  20,1,Twa Ha
  20,2,(Yewe Muhamadi) ntabwo twaguhishuriye Qur’an kugira ngo ikubere umuzigo
  20,3,Ahubwo (twayihishuye kugira ngo ibe) urwibutso kuri babandi batinya (Allah)
  20,4,(Iyo Qur’an) yahishuwe iturutse ku waremye isi n’ibirere bihanitse
  20,5,(Allah) Nyirimpuhwe aganje ku ntebe y’icyubahiro
  20,6,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi, n’ibiri hagati yabyondetse n’ibiri munsi y’ubutaka ni ibye"
  20,7,"Kandi n’ubwo warangurura ijwi (cyangwa ukavuga bucece, byose ni kimwe kuko) mu by’ukuri, (Allah) azi amabanga ndetse n’ibyihishe cyane (kurenza ayo mabanga)"
  20,8,Allah! Nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse we. Afite amazina meza
  20,9,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) waba waragezweho n’inkuru ya Musa
  20,10,"Ubwo yabonaga umuriro nuko akabwira ab’iwe ati \"Mugume aha! Mu by’ukuri, ndabutswe umuriro, hari ubwo nabazaniraho igishirira, cyangwa kuri uwo muriro nkahasanga uwatuyobora (inzira)"
  20,11,"Nuko awugezeho, yumva ijwi rimuhamagara riti \"Yewe Musa"
  20,12,"Mu by’ukuri, ndi Nyagasani wawe, bityo kwetura inkweto zawe kuko uri mu kibaya gitagatifu cya Tuwa"